    <string name="help_body">Enable Equalizer or any effect before opening media player.\n\nThe equalizer binds itself to the media player currently playing. Most media players allow other apps to apply effects, some require additional configuration, but some do not allow other apps to apply effects.\nConsequently, the equalizer may not bind to some media players and will bind to Global Mix to support them, e.g. YouTube (may not work on all devices).\n\nIf you use Youtube Music or Spotify, make sure to restart them while keeping the Equalizer or effect enabled.\n\nThe equalizer also shows a notification when it detects any media player; click it to bind the equalizer to that player.\n\nAlso, turn off battery optimization for this app to get the best experience.\n\nNow, play some music and enjoy!</string>
